## Email sent to DSpace users when they forget their password.
##
## Parameters: {0} is expanded to a special URL
##
## See org.dspace.core.Email for information on the format of this file.
##
#set($subject = "[papyrus.bib.umontreal.ca] - Change Password Request")
To change the password for your Papyrus account, please click the link below:

  ${params[0]}

If you need assistance with your account, please email depot@bib.umontreal.ca

The Papyrus Team
www.bib.umontreal.ca/Papyrus
